\sum_{k=0}^{i+1} \begin{pmatrix} i\\ k-1\end{pmatrix}
\sum_{k=0}^{i+1} \begin{pmatrix} i+1\\ k\end{pmatrix} = \sum_{k=0}^{i+1} (\begin{pmatrix} i\\ k\end{pmatrix} + \begin{pmatrix}i\\ k-1\end{pmatrix}) = 2^{i} + \sum_{k=0}^{i+1} \begin{pmatrix}i\\ k-1\end{pmatrix}
\sum_{k=0}^{i+1} (\begin{pmatrix} i\\ k\end{pmatrix} = 2^{i} 
